<item>
            <title>[LU-11779] interop: sanity-hsm test 255 fails with &apos;request on 0x200007935:0x268:0x0 is not SUCCEED on mds1&apos;</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11779</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;sanity-hsm test_255 was added to the Lustre test suites for &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11653&quot; title=&quot;hsm: copytool registration should trigger request dispatching from the coordinator&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-11653&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-11653&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; with patch &lt;a href=&quot;https://review.whamcloud.com/33649&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://review.whamcloud.com/33649&lt;/a&gt; . This test will fail for all Lustre servers with version less than 2.12.0. Thus, we need to add a version check for sanity-hsm test 255.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Similarly, sanity-hsm test 260c was modified by patch &lt;a href=&quot;https://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/33478/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/33478/&lt;/a&gt; to take advantage of the change implemented in &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11653&quot; title=&quot;hsm: copytool registration should trigger request dispatching from the coordinator&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-11653&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-11653&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; and, thus, test 260c should be skipped for servers less than 2.12.0.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
